# JobsGeParser core

- Single .NET 8 minimal API; one project in JobsGeParser.sln
- Read Readme.MD before structural changes
- DI: register in Ext.AddJobsGeService; keep Program.cs thin
- Endpoints: JobsGeParser.Endpoints, MapGroup("api/jobs/"), extension RegisterJobsEndpoints
- Parsing in HtmlProcessor; HTTP in JobsGeClient; storage in Repo (PostgreSQL via EF Core)
- Scraping runs via JobScrapeWorker BackgroundService — no manual POST retrieve endpoint
- Upsert by jobs.ge Id: insert / skip (unchanged) / update (changed fields)
- jobs.ge IT listings use JobsListUrl with cid=6
- Respect DetailPageDelayMs between detail-page requests
- DbContext and Repo are scoped; use IServiceScopeFactory in hosted services
- Do not add backup .csproj files or unrelated CI workflows
